---
import "@styles/global.module.css";
export const name = "Shutting Down TikTok";
export const description = "Akatsuki's TikTok shutdown, the reason behind it and why is she doing it.";
export const date = "2024-05-08";

import Header from "@components/header.astro";
import Footer from "@components/footer.astro";
import Meta from "@components/meta.astro";
import Scripts from "@components/scripts.astro";
import Cursor from "@components/cursor.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <Meta
            name="Shutting Down TikTok"
            description="Akatsuki's TikTok shutdown, the reason behind it and why is she doing it."
            tag=""
        />
        <Scripts />
        <Cursor />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <h1>Shutting Down TikTok</h1>
            <p>On May 8, 2024, TikTok came to a halt. The platform that once buzzed with short, snappy videos suddenly went silent. But why did this happen? The answer lies in a simple truth: making full-length YouTube videos is just easier for me.</p>
            <p>You see, while TikTok served its purpose for a while, I found myself constrained by its format. Sure, it was fun to create those quick clips, but as my projects grew, so did the need for more space and flexibility. YouTube provides that space, allowing me to express my ideas in full without the time constraints of TikTok.</p>
            <p>Now, I know what you're thinking. What about all those TikTok videos? Don't worry, I've got you covered. Every single one of those snippets will find a new home on my YouTube channel. So, if you're feeling nostalgic or simply want to relive some of those moments, you know where to find them.</p>
            <p>In the end, it's not about saying goodbye to TikTok, but rather embracing a new chapter in my creative journey. YouTube offers me the canvas I need to paint my ideas in full, and I'm excited to see where this transition takes us. So, join me on this new adventure, and let's make some magic together.</p>
            <p>Stay tuned, and let's keep creating!</p>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
